        public Statement getContentStatement()
        Gets the contentStatement value for this ExcludeContentFromContentBundle.
        Returns:
        contentStatement * The Publisher Query Language statement specifying which Content to exclude from the ContentBundle. The statement is expressed in terms of Content fields such as name and status.
